sentences: Proovinud olen seda juba varem ära teinud.
Ta on proovinud palju erinevaid meetodeid.
context: The word 'proovinud' is the Estonian past participle form of the verb 'proovima', which means 'to try'. It is formed by adding the -d suffix to the stem and indicates a completed action in the past. This form is typically used with the auxiliary verb 'olema' (to be) or sometimes with other verbs depending on context.
